{"tid":2145719,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"河北民企維權遭鎮壓噴椒","createTime":"2020-08-08T07:38:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T07:42:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e57956f103f0b45bab834adb3621e84bf1c2497a","tid":2145719,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:38:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200808/N2GEGDVHNGE4KM3LCN7ZTWRQWQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200808%2FN2GEGDVHNGE4KM3LCN7ZTWRQWQ%2F&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDMg3oUHlS2gCMg1IFosJMKY%3D&h=9002db99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200808%2FN2GEGDVHNGE4KM3LCN7ZTWRQWQ%2F&h=cb344d80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200808/N2GEGDVHNGE4KM3LCN7ZTWRQWQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n河北民企維權遭鎮壓噴椒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/c6yfVUgJXH-rWZ1F_JLWdrAXHJk=/190x151/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FMWHVLIMNUS3WHRXHRK3EEUIZQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fc6yfVUgJXH-rWZ1F_JLWdrAXHJk%3D%2F190x151%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFMWHVLIMNUS3WHRXHRK3EEUIZQ.gif&h=932f1cb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n河北保定爆發大型警民衝突！當地民企大午集團旗下農業公司員工，與國有農場發生土地糾紛，周二（4日）遭警方暴力鎮壓，員工被防暴警毆打、被催淚彈和辣椒水（圖）襲擊，多人受傷，包括集團創始人孫大午妻子在內39人一度被捕。集團創辦人孫大午在微博留言不怕惡勢力：「一個人害怕鬼，一群人站在一起就不再害怕，尤其是一群人舉起火把的時候！這就是大午人的苦難經！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n與國營農場土地糾紛<br />\n<br />\n外媒引述大午集團員工賈女士稱，徐水區郎五莊村的徐水區國營農場（原保定國營農場）無償佔該村數千畝土地，60多年來當地村民沒有任何收益，村民想收回土地，改由同樣位於該村的大午集團運營。周二凌晨，國營農場突然出動挖掘機拆除大午集團的臨時辦工室，又與前來阻止的村民和大午員工爆衝突。<br />\n<br />\n據指，大批防暴警隨即出動，使用催淚彈、辣椒水驅散大午員工，毆打令多人受傷。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台/有線新聞"},{"pid":"860b7cea7f1fa5d4bd1b50c86195c70039662f91","tid":2145719,"uid":42820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:39:15.000Z","msg":"又搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />收左美國佬幾多錢？"},{"pid":"74901370b10ff41571590b8ebf0ee64f76beaaae","tid":2145719,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:40:19.000Z","msg":"別添乱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"707f52a21141ec0337a415be10c88beabd4c661b","tid":2145719,"uid":329466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:41:24.000Z","msg":"收左美國佬錢?"},{"pid":"663063b158de38c2cd470b7d0cf6449121daf52d","tid":2145719,"uid":252142,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:42:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}